{"type":null,"faqId":10490,"title":"P6-U06   主屏幕简介","answer":"<h3 style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<span>1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">快速添加</span><span>/</span><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">删除主屏幕</span> \n</h3>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在主屏幕使用缩小手势，就可触发快速添加</span><span>/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">删除主屏幕。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31659\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"> </span>\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">图</span><span>1&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">编辑主屏幕</span> \n</p>\n<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">切换</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">2D/3D</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">界面：此产品不支持</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">3D</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">桌面，所以不支持切换</span><br />\n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">主菜单简介</span> \n</h3>\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\n\t<span>EmotionUI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">界面，主菜单即是</span><span>idle</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">界面，默认为四个屏幕，可以左右滑动来翻页。用户可以将应用程序和控件的快捷方式放置在主界面上，并可在主界面上点击图标启动应用程序。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">图</span><span>1.5.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">为开机主屏幕的截图，由上到下各标记为：</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\n\t<span>1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、信号栏区域；</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\n\t<span>2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、</span><span>MeWigdet</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">区域；</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\n\t<span>3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、桌面快捷方式；</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\n\t<span>4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、</span><span>dock</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">区域，放置应用程序的快捷方式，翻屏时该区域的应用快捷方式不随着移动。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">放置在主屏幕的元素可以是应用程序的快捷方式和窗口小部件。用户可以将一个应用程序的快捷方式拖动到已经放置快捷方式的位置，这样会形成一个文件夹，里面包含两个应用程序的快捷方式。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31661\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">图</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">2 </span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">主屏幕简介</span><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"> </span>\n</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<span>3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">编辑主菜单</span> \n</h3>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:黑体;\"><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">主屏幕上的快捷方式和窗口小部件都可以通过长按它触发编辑。编辑操作包括任意拖动，也可以拖动到图示位置</span><span>1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，触发卸载应用将其删除。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31662\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"> </span>\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">注意</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">：系统关键应用是无法删除的</span> \n</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<span>4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">如何添加快捷图标到桌面</span> \n</h3>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">长按主屏幕空白处或者按菜单键触发，选择进入窗口小工具。长按一个窗口小工具，将其拖动到桌面空白处即可。</span> \n</p>\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31663\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>\n<br />\n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"></span> \n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":0,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1225","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1397629229000,"seriesProductName":"EDGE-U00","visitedTimes":54,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}